videos.headline: App State QB fakes, dives at the pylon for TD
videos.description: Appalachian State QB Zac Thomas fakes a handoff and rushes 7 yards to the corner of the end zone for the first touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (App State QB fakes, dives at the pylon for TD) 2019/10/9

videos.headline: Louisiana ties it up right before the half
videos.description: Levi Lewis pump fakes and fires a pass to Nick Ralston for a 14-yard touchdown to tie App State in the final seconds of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisiana ties it up right before the half) 2019/10/9
